headline: Did Record Gas Derivatives Volumes Just Shift Intercontinental Exchange's (ICE) Investment Narrative?
summary: Earlier this month, Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. launched TTF Daily Options on its front‑month TTF natural gas futures and reported record 2025 trading activity across TTF and JKM LNG contracts, including more than 100 million TTF futures and options traded and record open interest in both markets. This surge in natural gas derivatives activity highlights how ICE’s deepening role in global energy benchmarks can influence liquidity, hedging behavior, and demand for its trading...
